;; 2d8+6 damage, and the target is marked until the end of the dreadguard’s next turn. &lt;/p&gt;]]; [[/roll 2d8+6#&lt;p style=\"background-color:green;color:white;\"&gt;(⚔) &lt;b&gt;Mace&lt;/b&gt; (standard, at-will) ✦ &lt;b&gt;Weapon&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Reach 2; +29 vs AC; 2d8+6 damage, and the target is marked until the end of the dreadguard’s next turn. &lt;/p&gt;]] <15>  damage, and the target is marked until the end of the dreadguard’s next turn. </p></tr></td><tr><td><h4><b>Triggered</b></h4></td></tr><tr><td><p style=\"background-color:green;color:white;\">[[/roll 0#&lt;p style=\"background-color:green;color:white;\"&gt; &lt;b&gt;Death Guardian&lt;/b&gt; (immediate interrupt, when an enemy marked by the dreadguard makes an attack that does not include the dreadguard; at-will) &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;The dreadguard makes a mace attack against the triggering enemy.&lt;/p&gt;]]  <b>Death Guardian</b> (immediate interrupt, when an enemy marked by the dreadguard makes an attack that does not include the dreadguard; at-will) </p><p>The dreadguard makes a mace attack against the triggering enemy.</p></tr></td><tr><td><h4><b>Free</b></h4></td></tr><tr><td><p style=\"background-color:green;color:white;\">[[/roll 0#&lt;p style=\"background-color:green;color:white;\"&gt; &lt;b&gt;Soul Shield&lt;/b&gt; (free, when an ally within 5 squares is hit by an attack; at-will) &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;The dreadguard expends one soul shard and the ally gains a +4 bonus to all defenses against the attack.&lt;/p&gt;]]  <b>Soul Shield</b> (free, when an ally within 5 squares is hit by an attack; at-will) </p><p>The dreadguard expends one soul shard and the ally gains a +4 bonus to all defenses against the attack.</p></tr></td><tr><td><h4><b>Minor</b></h4></td></tr><tr><td><p style=\"background-color:green;color:white;\">[[/roll 0#&lt;p style=\"background-color:green;color:white;\"&gt; &lt;b&gt;Consume Soul Shard&lt;/b&gt; (minor; at-will) ✦ &lt;b&gt;Healing&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;The dreadguard expends one soul shard and regains 20 hit points.&lt;/p&gt;]]  <b>Consume Soul Shard</b> (minor; at-will) ✦ <b>Healing</b></p><p>The dreadguard expends one soul shard and regains 20 hit points.</p></tr></td><tr><td><h4><b>-</b></h4></td></tr><tr><td><p style=\"background-color:green;color:white;\">[[/roll 0#&lt;p style=\"background-color:green;color:white;\"&gt; &lt;b&gt;Soul Shroud&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;The soul shroud contains soul shards that swirl around the dreadguard to protect and empower it. At the start of an encounter, the soul shroud contains four soul shards. While the soul shroud is depleted of soul shards, the dreadguard takes a –2 penalty to attack rolls.&lt;/p&gt;]]  <b>Soul Shroud</b></p><p>The soul shroud contains soul shards that swirl around the dreadguard to protect and empower it. At the start of an encounter, the soul shroud contains four soul shards. While the soul shroud is depleted of soul shards, the dreadguard takes a –2 penalty to attack rolls.</p></tr></td></table>",
